% Regression test: goal with variables should NOT produce trivial proof.
%
% Bug: _deny_goals() only flips literal signs, doesn't Skolemize.
% Result: denied goal -P(x) matches P(a) trivially via x->a.
% Expected: denied goal -P(c1) does NOT match P(a) since c1 != a.

formulas(sos).
  P(a).
end_of_list.

formulas(goals).
  P(x).
end_of_list.
